00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:07.311
the plan is to find the Japanese somewhere in the middle.

00:01:07.411 --> 00:01:08.843
[LOOKING FOR THEIR PREY]

00:01:08.991 --> 00:01:12.071
The Japanese Whaling Fleet is again heading to the Southern Ocean.

00:01:12.225 --> 00:01:17.363
They've target this year 945 minke and fin whales.

00:01:17.401 --> 00:01:18.384
The hunt is on.

00:01:20.576 --> 00:01:22.273
[SOME CALL THEM PIRATES]

00:01:25.250 --> 00:01:26.995
